The two Tundra Yeti Caves in DreadLands provide about 1 yellow bubble per two hours for a level 44 mage. About 50% of spawn are green, some are high green and still give exp.<br>
Tundra Yeti are level 31 - 33<br>
Locations<br>
pos 2000 pos 5000<br>
and<br>
neg 2000 pos 3500<br>
<br>
Spawn is easy for solo with a near max level earth pet with fire shield. Nuking is required.<br>
<br>
(Focus item used and pet hits for 46)<br>
<br>
Dadijob<br>
Level 44 mage<br>
Prexus<br>
:Rollin<br>
